					<h3 class="text-xl font-black lg:text-3x2 uppercase text-black pb-0">our approach</h3>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-black lg:text-3x2 uppercase text-gray pb-0">peace of mind</h3>
				<span class="thin-text text-gray">24%</span>
				<div class="border-t border-red ml-8 "><p>&nbsp;</p></div>
				<p class="pb-12 text-black"><span class="font-bold">Tarmac Surfacing Experts - </span>Our journey began in road construction, but we've evolved into true specialists in macadam surfacing. Our experience is our strength, forming the bedrock of our expertise. Whether we're crafting beautiful driveways or constructing sturdy roads, we bring a wealth of knowledge to every project.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
		<img src="/bomag-asphalt-roller-yell.webp" alt="Bomag Tarmac Roller" class="md:h-40 md:w-40 h-20 w-20" />	  
		<div class="grid grid-rows-2">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-2">
			<div class="bg-black h-4 min-h-0"></div>
			<div class="bg-red h-4 min-h-0"></div>
			</div>
			<div class="grid grid-cols-3">
			<div class="bg-gray-light h-4 min-h-0"></div>
			<div class="bg-white h-4 min-h-0"></div>
			<div class="bg-gray-dark h-4 min-h-0"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!--end of how we work -->
		<div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center items-center pb-4 pt-24">
			<p class="v-copy2">questions?</p>
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-red mt-9">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 17.25 12 21m0 0-3.75-3.75M12 21V3" />
			</svg>
		</div>
		<!--questions -->
		<h2 class="text-right uppercase text-lg text-gray pb-4 font-bold">questions that our clients often ask</h2>
		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-0.5">
			<div class="bg-red rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex place-items-center justify-end w-full h-full min-h-96 pb-52 lg:pb-2">
				<h3 class="text-white text-6xl font-bold -rotate-90 origin-bottom-right uppercase">pricing</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-gray p-4 rounded-lg min-h-96">
				<h3 class="uppercase text-3xl text-white">spec</h3>
				<RedLine />
				<p class="text-white text-sm md:text-base">Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas. Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas. Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas. Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas. Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas. Checkout our handy work from driveways and roads to car parks and communal areas.</p>	
			</div>
			<div class="bg-gray-dark rounded-lg overflow-hidden flex place-items-center justify-end w-full h-full min-h-96 pb-72 lg:pb-16">
				<h3 class="text-white text-6xl font-bold -rotate-90 origin-bottom-right uppercase">Process</h3>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-black p-4 rounded-lg min-h-96">
				<p class="v-copy-ans text-lg text-white">Mrs S Reed – Kent</p>
				<p class="text-white font-bold lg:text-2xl text-xl pb-6">“I am writing to thank you and your team formally and personally for helping to ensure that the major project undertaken by the school this summer was a success.”</p>
				<img src="ukc.svg" class="md:w-[6rem] h-12 ml-auto"alt="university of kent tarmac review">
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center items-center pb-4 pt-28">
			<p class="v-copy2">understanding tarmac</p>
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-red mt-24">
				<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 17.25 12 21m0 0-3.75-3.75M12 21V3" />
			</svg>
		</div>
    </div>	  
	<!-- end of main tile content-->
    <div class="border-l border-gray-light border-solid w-12 pt-40">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor" class="w-12 h-12 text-red">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m8.25 4.5 7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
        </svg> 
    </div>
</div>
<!-- blog archive-->
<div class="w-full md:h-[47.75rem] bg-white grid md:grid-cols-4 md:grid-rows-4 grid-cols-2 grid-rows-6 gap-0.5 px-0.5">
	<div class="row-span-1 col-span-1 rounded-lg bg-[url('/tarmac-car-park.webp')] bg-no-repeat"></div>
	<div class="row-span-1 col-span-1 rounded-lg bg-gray-dark p-4 text-white">
